Reatil Sales Dashboard
This projects an interactive analysing retail sales performance,profitability and customer segements
🛠 Tools Used
Power BI
Excel
📈 Key Insights
West region generates the highest sales
Technology category is the top-performing segment
Discounts have a negative impact on profit in some areas
Consumer segment contributes the largest share of revenue
📌 Features
KPI cards for Sales, Profit, Quantity, Discount
Regional and category-based analysis
Interactive filters (Region, Category, Segment)
Scatter analysis of Discount vs Profit
